{"tid":2186611,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：忠實讀者689 數漏《蘋果》廣告（李八方）","createTime":"2020-09-03T05:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T05:38:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"253e214bf1f850bb1e18b9ce1ee90052a135c27c","tid":2186611,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T05:38:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/WILVFCDSRNE5JKI7U4K3G6NJPY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FWILVFCDSRNE5JKI7U4K3G6NJPY%2F&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hdey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=b5048de3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200903%2FWILVFCDSRNE5JKI7U4K3G6NJPY%2F&h=2a44b5fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200903/WILVFCDSRNE5JKI7U4K3G6NJPY/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：忠實讀者689 數漏《蘋果》廣告（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PYheULu1Xjf1oSDYewkrS4LNDRE=/999x879/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BANUKLKFKJBRVCND7V25UNWBLA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPYheULu1Xjf1oSDYewkrS4LNDRE%3D%2F999x879%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBANUKLKFKJBRVCND7V25UNWBLA.jpg&h=496b4148&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■梁振英噚日睇漏全版黃到金嘅廣告，即俾網民恥笑。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。作為《蘋果》最忠實讀者，689慣晒每日用8秒睇《蘋果》然後數有幾多版廣告，但唔知係咪呢排廣告太多數唔切，搞到佢連生活習慣都改變埋，自此冇再每日數《蘋果》廣告，直至佢噚日出山「重操故業」，點知頭炮即出事俾網民恥笑。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無視全版黃到金<br />\n<br />\n689噚日重出江湖，喺朝早9點01分就喺fb度出帖，話《蘋果》「回復常態」，咁咩係《蘋果》常態呢？原來就係「沒有任何全版廣告」！咦，照咁睇，689原來喺失職期間，係有繼續日日睇《蘋果》，只不過係報憂不報喜，唔講《蘋果》全版廣告成績啫！之不過，689唔知係咪太耐冇做好「廣告專員」工作，報紙A7頁明明有全版黃到金嘅廣告，由「一群婚禮界同路人」刊登，表明撐「言論自由」，但689就直接無視囉！有網民恥笑佢唔知係咪只掛住驗毒所以冇去驗眼，又有人話689係咪好似啲長者咁，俾騙徒呃，買咗份假蘋果呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUnjgAg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUnjgAg.jpg&h=1c7e2ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果呢？"}]}